data.description: New Price Improvement and seller offering $10,000 to a buyer to use for rate buy down or closing costs. Welcome to your dream home in an exclusive guard gated community. This stunning 5-bedroom, 4 1/2 bathroom, 3 car garage residence is situated on a spacious corner lot, offering a perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and convenience. As you enter, you are greeted by the elegant dining room, providing ample space for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories. The adjacent flex space, equipped with private French doors, serves as an ideal home office or versatile living area. The heart of the home is undoubtedly the gourmet kitchen, boasting 42-inch cabinets, granite counters, a decorator backsplash, built-in oven and microwave, 5-burner cooktop, pot filler, vent hood, and a large island that seamlessly flows into the family room. The kitchen also features a generous walk-in pantry and a Butlers pantry, ensuring both style and functionality for the discerning chef. The dinette area, overlooking the lush backyard, provides a perfect spot for casual meals or morning coffee. The family room with a gorgeous ceiling and surround sound is seamlessly connected to the kitchen and creates an inviting space for family and friends to gather. Step outside to the covered lanai where you can unwind after a long day while enjoying the surround sound. The main floor hosts the luxurious primary bedroom, offering a tranquil retreat with an impressive walk-in closet and a spa-like bathroom. The primary bath is equipped with a large walk-in shower, a relaxing tub, and 2 vanities, creating a serene oasis for relaxation. Upstairs, discover a sprawling loft area with surround sound, offering endless possibilities. Two bedrooms on one side of the loft share a bathroom while the other 2 bedrooms on the other side of the loft each have a private bath which provides privacy and comfort for all. Additional features include pull down stairs for attic access, irrigation system, pendant lighting wiring in kitchen, recessed lighting, and exquisite tray ceilings that add a touch of sophistication. Beyond the confines of this luxurious abode, the community offers a abundance of amenities, including pools, clubhouse, tennis courts, pickleball courts, basketball courts, boat slips, club house with restaurant, fitness center with free classes, and many clubs you can join. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own!
